;How Lightbeam Works
Takaa kaŋ nda Lightbeam ga dira


;Download and run the Lightbeam add-on in your Firefox browser.
Lightbeam tonton zumandi nd'a dirandi war Firefox ceecikaa ra.


;Lightbeam will create a record of events for every site you visit and every third party site that is stored locally on your browser.
Lightbeam ga taariki tee nungu foo kul kaŋ war n'a guna batey se nda nungu waani foo kul kaŋ jisandi war ceecikaa ra.


;Lightbeam visually graphs these events to highlight the interactions between sites you intentionally visit and the third parties.
Lightbeam ka batey wey cebe nda biiyaŋ hala war ma dii nungey kaŋ war cerecere k'i guna nda nungu waaney kaŋ ga dobu i ga.


;Lightbeam will continue to add to your graph as you browse the Web. You can stop Lightbeam at any time by disabling it or uninstalling the add-on. Your Lightbeam data can be easily saved or deleted.
Waati kaŋ war ga interneti naaru, Lightbeam ga gaabandi ka tonton war šilbayyan biyoo ga. War ga hin ka Lightbeam kayandi waati kul wala tontonoo dogu k'a kaa. War ga hin ka war Lightbeam bayhayey jiši wal'i tuusu nda faala.


;Tracking & privacy
Ganayan nda sutura


;Not all tracking is bad. Many services rely on user data to provide relevant content and enhance your online experience.
Manti ganayan kul ma laala. Goymee booboyaŋ ga gundekuna himante zaa borey ga wala ceeciyan boryandi war se interneti ra.


;But tracking can happen without the user’s knowledge.
Amma ganayan ga hin ka bila nda goykaa ma bay.


;That’s not okay for some.
Ir se woo šii fondo ra.


;It should be you who decides when, how and if you want your browsing data to be shared. We recognize the importance of transparency and our mission is all about empowering users — both with tools and information.
A ši hima kala war no ma tabatandi waati kaŋ war ga boona ka war ceeciyan bayhayey žemni. Ir ga bay kaŋ hayey kaarandiroo nd'ir anniyaa kul ti goykey ma sahãndi ngi almuraadey ra — ka tee goyjinawey nd'alhabarey.


;Explore the database
