;In the Lightbeam database, you will be able to browse first and third-party connection data uploaded by donors who use the Lightbeam add-on.
Lightbeam bayrayhaya hugoo ra, war ga hin ka dii war boŋ wala boro waani dobuyan bayhayey kaŋ kanbuzaakey n'i noo ka goy nda Lightbeam tontonoo.


;We’re building this crowd-sourced directory to encourage users to visualize the state of tracking as an aggregate and to examine relationships that exist on the Web.
Ir goo ma goy nda jamaa aššil-maašeede ga goykey biney dam ka dii ganayan alhaaloo sanda marga nda cettekašinay kaŋ ga bangay interneti koroši ka boori. 


;Visualize your data
