;As a part of Lightbeam, we are creating a big-picture view of Internet tracking and of how first and third party sites are connected.
Ir anniya foo Lightbeam se ti bii-beero gunari kaŋ ir goo m'a tee interneti ganayan se ka dii takaa kaŋ nda boro boŋ nungey nda nungu waaney ga dobu cere ga.


;To help us, you can contribute your data to our Lightbeam database.
War ga hin ka war bayhayey sanba Lightbeam bayrayhaya hugoo do k'ir faaba.


